description:
Service Usage

This service is currently pushing new and updated Health cases that are of interest to Settlement processing. This is primarily for Refugee and Humanitarian cases but could be extended to meet other demands of the settlement process. The Health Case sent is a small subset of available Health Case data but includes question and answer sets from available health exams.

Service Usage

This service is currently pushing new and updated Health cases that are of interest to Settlement processing. This is primarily for Refugee and Humanitarian cases but could be extended to meet other demands of the settlement process. The Health Case sent is a small subset of available Health Case data but includes question and answer sets from available health exams.

Service Composition

This services is not composed of any other services.

Transformation

No transformations are done on this service.
